  "story": "A deeply moving Hindi bhajan celebrating God's overflowing grace. This traditional hymn reminds believers that salvation is entirely a gift of God's unmerited favor. It is widely sung in churches, home fellowships, and prayer meetings across North India, touching hearts with its simple yet profound message of grace upon grace.",
